    <div class="crowd-tip"><strong>Best time:</strong> Weekday departures in June or July allow the trail to be completed in the midnight sun with minimal other hikers. Even at peak season this trail is far quieter than the Nordkapp plateau — most visitors do not attempt it. Start early or in the evening to avoid the midday cruise-ship peak at the nearby Nordkapp car park.</div>
